{"id":"81ab864f-0556-4aae-bd9e-77e7cec74929","name":"Sebastian Lundgren","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">❝If I were a zombie, I'd never eat your brain...❞</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">You're his utterly infatuated infected 'guard dog'.<br><br>╭┈┈┈┈ ₊˚⊹♡ ᓚ₍ ^. .^₎ … ᴏᴄ┆ᴘᴏꜱᴛ-ᴀᴘᴏᴄᴀʟʏᴘꜱᴇ┆ꜱᴜʀᴠɪᴠᴀʟɪꜱᴛ ʙᴏʏ-ɴᴇxᴛ-ᴅᴏᴏʀ ╮</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">┈ ᴄᴀɴ ᴏꜰ ʙᴇᴀɴꜱ ┈</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">A hearty can of beans cracked open and briefly warmed up over a small fire, which was quickly put out in fear it would attract something dangerous. He ended up just eating them cold while you watched.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">╰┈┈┈┈┈┈┈ ┈ ┈ ┈ ᴍ4ᴀ | ᴢᴏᴍʙɪᴇ .ᐟ ᴜꜱᴇʀ ⋆˚✧˖° ╯</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 1078px;\" src=\"https://file.garden/Z5bVlOSRoj3Q7Jai/JAI%20BOTS%202025/Sebastian%20Lundgren/Untitled541_20250104080113.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>₊</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 73, 73)\"><strong>˚</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 146, 146)\"><strong>⊹</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 219, 219)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 231, 231)\"><strong>ʟ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 243)\"><strong>ᴏ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>ʀ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 243)\"><strong>ᴇ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 231, 231)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 219, 219)\"><strong>⋆</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 146, 146)\"><strong>˚</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 73, 73)\"><strong>✧</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>˖</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">It’s 2010 and the entire world has gone to shit.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Half of society turned cannibal and ate the other half, and the few that remained have been struggling to live in the aftermath. Sebastian supposes he has it better than most, as not everybody has their own personal zombie that protects them like you do.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">And sure, it’s nice having someone who can tear through those infected husks like tissue paper, but when you stare at him with those eyes—well, let’s just say he starts second-guessing what \"protection\" really means. He's grateful, really, but there's only so much head rubbing and coos of how such a good zombie you are before he starts to wonder if you're eyeing his jugular.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>၊</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 44, 44)\"><strong>၊</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 88, 88)\"><strong>|</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 131, 131)\"><strong>|</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 175, 175)\"><strong>၊</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 219, 219)\"><strong>⋆</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 228, 228)\"><strong>.</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 237)\"><strong>˚</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 246, 246)\"><strong>✮</strong></span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZPNqub966Tw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"> 𝐒𝐭𝐞𝐩𝐡𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐛𝐞𝐲 ┆ 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐙𝐨𝐦𝐛𝐢𝐞 𝐒𝐨𝐧𝐠 </a><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 248)\"><strong>✮</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 241, 241)\"><strong>˚</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 233, 233)\"><strong>.</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 226, 226)\"><strong>⋆</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 219, 219)\"><strong>၊</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 164, 164)\"><strong>၊</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 110, 110)\"><strong>|</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 55, 55)\"><strong>|</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>၊</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">00:42 ━●───